title: 254 - Free Vasectomy
description:
ET starts today’s podcast with the quote: ”Excellence is what we repeatedly do.” Over the weekend, CJ celebrated his bday and ET bought him a gift that he never received. ET turns this disappointment into an object lesson for people who want massive success, but their energy and effort don’t match their dreams and goals. While listening to this podcast the guys put emphasis on the importance of being excellent at all times. You can’t make next level money with average service and energy, grab your pen and pads; this one gets deep.
